caption:
About last night... we kicked off London Fashion Week with a bang, celebrating YOU, our amazing community of #humansofrixo at our Kings road store with! The atmosphere was buzzing as we danced, laughed, and showcased our favorite RIXO looks from past and present, including some fabulous old RIXO gems!♥️

Nights like this remind us how lucky we are to have such a vibrant community. A massive thank you to everyone who joined the fun—your spirit made it truly unforgettable! 💫

If you missed out on getting your tickets, sign up via the link in our bio to be the first to hear about our upcoming events and parties. We can’t wait to celebrate with you next time! 💥
